description: For sale: $224,900. Just over 5 acres of unparalleled peace and quiet! Wildlife, nature, and tranquility at its best! Whether you're listening to a babbling brook or the sounds of birds, you'll find it all here. There are a few buildings and a home on the property, but all are considered a tear down. Located less than an hour from Minneapolis/Saint Paul, Rochester, and even Mankato, this is truly a prime location and a rare find piece of land. Septic, updated well, fully landscaped and ready for your attention and care, to make your own little piece of paradise. Perfect for your hobby farm. Half mile to tar roads and in coveted Nerstrand school district and close to Northfield schools.

description: Recently sold: $300,000. Welcome home to 24 acres of beautiful land with hundreds of mature Trees and a large rolling pasture. This very cute ranch style home  has been tastefully updated and includes many wall mounted TV's, an electric fireplace, reclaimed barn wood accents, tile floors, a large HOT TUB, a designated spot for the above ground pool, and there are also many outbuildings. One of the large buildings is currently a workshop with wood and gas heat, and one of the other outbuildings could easily be transformed into a art studio or kids play house!! The large quonset hut is perfect for horses or a few head of cattle, and the lot itself is feed lot certified. New septic was just installed and was sized for a 4 bedroom home if you want to add more living space. This property is located in a beautiful area and the land itself inspires peace!!

description: Recently sold: $314,000. Horse enthusiasts and cattle farmers beware! Excellent hobby farm opportunity including 8 acres or optional 12 additional tillable/pasture acres for your new farm. Multiple outbuildings, barn, machine sheds, green-house, pole shed and more. Great sized 2 story farm house with several updates including large heated garage. New septic, newer AC. Northfield schools. Great location only 10 minutes from Northfield, Dennison or Nerstrand. Great opportunity!

Recently sold: $305,000. Storybook farmhouse nestled on 2 acres with mature trees and shrubs, surrounded by meadow, cropland, rolling hills, creek and woods.  Large rooms with lots of windows, main floor laundry, lots of storage, 14' x 16' shed with loft, several flower gardens, large vegetable garden, fruit trees and other small fruits.  Quiet, private, close to state park, in Northfield school district, gorgeous views, well maintained and lovingly cared for.

Recently sold: $320,000. Charming and picturesque hobby farm in an idyllic private setting, with a large barn and acreage for animals and outdoor activities. The lovingly restored historic farmhouse is set far back from a quiet gravel road near Big Woods State Park, close to Northfield/Faribault/Kenyon, just 45 minutes to Rochester, and less than an hour to downtown Minneapolis or St. Paul. Hardwood floors, beautiful woodwork, and new Marvin windows throughout, custom kitchen with cherry cabinets. Spacious bedrooms, cozy and light-filled sun room with gas fireplace/stove, wood-burning stove in living room, and a wonderful patio for outdoor dining and entertaining. Set up for horses, with new high-tensile and wood fencing and outdoor riding arena.
